  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluated the association between HMGB1 and diastolic dysfunction in hypertensive
      patients. HMGB1 level were tested in all patients, and diastolic function determined by
      echocardiographic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
